CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

Appellant has not filed a memorandum in support of jurisdiction, due February 22, 2019, in compliance with the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio and therefore has failed to prosecute this cause with the requisite diligence. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.
